OL,6,FA motorist who seriously injured a
OL,7,Fchild in Kent while driving under the
OL,8,Finfluence of drugs has been jailed.
OL,10,FDanny Butt was driving his Seat Leon
OL,11,Fin Woodlands Road, Gillingham, in
OL,12,Fexcess of the 30mph speed limit in
OL,13,FJune 2022.
OL,15,FHe then drove through a red traffic
OL,16,Flight at the junction with Cornwallis
OL,17,FAvenue and struck a 10-year-old boy
OL,18,Fwho had started to cross the road.
