OL,4,Cdriving under the influence of drugs
OL,6,FThe child suffered serious head
OL,7,Finjuries and was taken to hospital by
OL,8,Fair ambulance.
OL,10,FButt was arrested at the scene and
OL,11,Fprovided a specimen of blood for
OL,12,Fanalysis which proved he had been
OL,13,Fdriving whilst over the prescribed
OL,14,Flimit for cannabis and also showed the
OL,15,Fpresence of cocaine.
OL,17,FButt, of Talma Road, Brixton, London,
OL,18,Fwas charged with causing serious
OL,19,Finjury by dangerous driving and
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty at Maidstone Crown
OL,21,FCourt.
