OL,6,FThe 42-year-old was sentenced to three
OL,7,Fyears and 10 months' imprisonment.
OL,9,FHe will be disqualified from driving
OL,10,Ffor three years when he is released
OL,11,Ffrom prison and will have to take an
OL,12,Fextended retest.
OL,14,FSerious collision investigator,
OL,15,FDetective Constable Lee Berridge,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Butt got behind the wheel of a
OL,17,Fcar knowing he was unfit to drive due
OL,18,Fto his misuse of controlled drugs.
