OL,6,F"He would have realised he posed a
OL,7,Frisk to other road users and
OL,8,Fpedestrians but proceeded,
OL,9,Fnonetheless, to drive in a very
OL,10,Fdangerous manner.
OL,12,F"Furthermore, Butt intentionally tried
OL,13,Fto beat a red traffic light and this
OL,14,Freckless decision has altered the path
OL,15,Fof a young child's future.
OL,17,F"His victim suffered appalling
OL,18,Finjuries and is gradually recovering
OL,19,Fwhilst making adjustment to his day to
OL,20,Fday life and receiving ongoing medical
OL,21,Fassessments.
